msgid "Tron-like Game"
msgstr "Igra nalik na tron"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.ksnakeduel.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KSnakeDuel is a simple Tron-Clone. You can play KSnakeDuel against the "
"computer or a friend. The aim of the game is to live longer than your "
"opponent. To do that, avoid running into a wall, your own tail and that of "
"your opponent."
msgstr ""
"K‑zmijski-dvoboj je jednostavan klon trona. Možete igrati protiv računara "
"ili prijatelja. Cilj partije je nadživeti svog protivnika. To činite "
"izbegavanjem sudara sa zidom, sopstvenim repom ili repom protivnika."
